## Project Overview
This project is a college FAQ chatbot built using 
Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). It answers student 
questions about admissions, fees, hostel, exams, and placements.

## Tech Stack
- Backend: Python + FastAPI
- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS
- RAG: LangChain + ChromaDB
- LLM: Groq API (llama-3.1-8b-instant)
- Embeddings: sentence-transformers (local, free)

